trans-unit.source: Implements the basic functionality for a collection of table layout styles.
trans-unit.target: Implementa a funcionalidade básica para uma coleção de estilos de layout de tabela.

trans-unit.source: The TableLayoutStyleCollection class represents the collection of all the styles used to describe the columns or rows in an associated <xref:System.Windows.Forms.TableLayoutPanel>.
trans-unit.target: A classe TableLayoutStyleCollection representa a coleção de todos os estilos usados para descrever as colunas ou linhas em um associado <xref:System.Windows.Forms.TableLayoutPanel>.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.TableLayoutPanel>

trans-unit.source: Classes derived from TableLayoutStyleCollection are specialized as follows: - A <xref:System.Windows.Forms.TableLayoutColumnStyleCollection> aggregates column styles as a collection of <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ColumnStyle> objects.
trans-unit.target: Classes derivadas de TableLayoutStyleCollection são especializadas da seguinte maneira: - um <xref:System.Windows.Forms.TableLayoutColumnStyleCollection>agrega estilos de coluna como uma coleção de <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ColumnStyle>objetos.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.ColumnStyle> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.TableLayoutColumnStyleCollection>

trans-unit.source: - A <xref:System.Windows.Forms.TableLayoutRowStyleCollection> aggregates row styles as a collection of <xref:System.Windows.Forms.RowStyle> objects.
trans-unit.target: -A <xref:System.Windows.Forms.TableLayoutRowStyleCollection>agregações estilos de linha como uma coleção de <xref:System.Windows.Forms.RowStyle>objetos.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.RowStyle> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.TableLayoutRowStyleCollection>

trans-unit.source: Most of the members of TableLayoutStyleCollection are implementations of <xref:System.Collections.IList>.
trans-unit.target: A maioria dos membros de TableLayoutStyleCollection são implementações de <xref:System.Collections.IList>.</xref:System.Collections.IList>

trans-unit.target: Adiciona um novo <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.TableLayoutStyle"> </xref> ao final da coleção atual.

trans-unit.source: The Add method reapplies the table layout to all the controls in the current <xref:System.Windows.Forms.TableLayoutPanel> container.
trans-unit.target: O método Add reaplica o layout da tabela para todos os controles no atual <xref:System.Windows.Forms.TableLayoutPanel>contêiner.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.TableLayoutPanel>

trans-unit.target: O número de estilos armazenados em uma coleção é limitado apenas pela memória disponível.

trans-unit.source: The Clear method performs two main actions: - It disassociates the current <xref:System.Windows.Forms.TableLayoutStyleCollection> from its <xref:System.Windows.Forms.TableLayoutPanel> container so that the styles are no longer applied to the layout of the controls contained within the panel.
trans-unit.target: O método Clear executa duas ações principais:--desassocia atual <xref:System.Windows.Forms.TableLayoutStyleCollection>de seu <xref:System.Windows.Forms.TableLayoutPanel>contêiner para que os estilos são não mais aplicada para o layout dos controles contidos dentro do painel.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.TableLayoutPanel> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.TableLayoutStyleCollection>

trans-unit.source: As a result, the table layout is reapplied to all the controls in the panel.
trans-unit.target: Como resultado, o layout da tabela é reaplicado a todos os controles no painel.
